              "free_text": [
                " Separation of spin-flip from nonspin-flip",
                " on transmission through iron filters.",
                "Spin-flip and non-spin-flip neutron intensities were",
                " measured at 6 scattering angles",
                " ranging from 15 to 65 degs."
              ]
            }
          ],
