          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The spin-flip and non-spin-flip cross-sections were",
                "summed to give the total cross-section.",
                "A slight decrease of the non-spin-flip (and hence the",
                "total) cross-section with scattering vector was ob-",
                "served, which was however neglected for the present",
                "consideration of the isotropic contribution.",
                "The measured cross-sections (at high scattering",
                "vectors), after correction, were",
                "         spin-flip            20 millibarn/sr,atom",
                "         non-spin-flip       120 millibarn/sr,atom"
              ]
            }
          ],
